WEBVTT

00:01:35.870 --> 00:01:41.000 line:80%
[Pursuit of Jade]

00:01:41.130 --> 00:01:43.790 line:80%
[Episode 9]

00:01:44.140 --> 00:01:47.540 line:80%
[Xigu Lane]

00:01:45.110 --> 00:01:47.279 line:80%
Dry weather!

00:01:47.890 --> 00:01:50.589 line:80%
Beware of fire!

00:01:56.750 --> 00:01:58.750 line:80%
I have experience in these matters.

00:01:59.870 --> 00:02:01.680 line:80%
There's no need to rush it.

00:02:02.150 --> 00:02:04.280 line:80%
Silly girl, what do you know?

00:02:05.280 --> 00:02:06.920 line:80%
Men's prime is shorter than women's,

00:02:06.920 --> 00:02:07.640 line:80%
you know?

00:02:08.160 --> 00:02:11.080 line:80%
When young, they have the desire
but not the guts

00:02:11.200 --> 00:02:12.460 line:80%
because they're poor.

00:02:12.640 --> 00:02:13.600 line:80%
In their prime,

00:02:13.600 --> 00:02:14.990 line:80%
they have the guts but not the desire

00:02:14.990 --> 00:02:16.250 line:80%
because they're busy.

00:02:16.830 --> 00:02:19.080 line:80%
By the time they have
both the desire and the guts,

00:02:19.080 --> 00:02:20.410 line:80%
the abilities are gone.

00:02:21.480 --> 00:02:23.310 line:80%
So you must act early

00:02:23.330 --> 00:02:24.930 line:80%
in order to have good babies.

00:02:26.830 --> 00:02:27.990 line:80%
Mrs. Zhao.

00:02:29.190 --> 00:02:30.230 line:80%
Fine.

00:02:30.879 --> 00:02:32.540 line:80%
Let me give you another trick.

00:02:33.920 --> 00:02:36.230 line:80%
During the day, I washed the bedding

00:02:36.830 --> 00:02:38.480 line:80%
you use on the floor.

00:02:40.050 --> 00:02:42.650 line:80%
He won't let you
sleep on the bare floor, right?

00:03:30.920 --> 00:03:31.640 line:80%
Come here.

00:03:33.879 --> 00:03:34.390 line:80%
Me?

00:03:35.430 --> 00:03:36.830 line:80%
Why would I go there?

00:03:39.230 --> 00:03:40.560 line:80%
There's only one quilt.

00:03:41.270 --> 00:03:42.600 line:80%
If you don't sleep here,

00:03:42.950 --> 00:03:44.550 line:80%
you're going to catch a cold.

00:03:45.640 --> 00:03:47.100 line:80%
I'm not afraid of the cold.

00:03:58.360 --> 00:03:58.960 line:80%
Come here.

00:04:12.270 --> 00:04:13.870 line:80%
If you don't come sleep here,

00:04:14.610 --> 00:04:16.740 line:80%
Mrs. Zhao won't sleep a wink all night.

00:04:24.750 --> 00:04:26.630 line:80%
Just as I predicted.

00:04:27.380 --> 00:04:29.110 line:80%
She has to sleep in the bed.

00:04:29.570 --> 00:04:31.430 line:80%
You always come up with bad ideas.

00:04:31.430 --> 00:04:32.400 line:80%
If she really freezes,

00:04:32.400 --> 00:04:34.360 line:80%
I'll have to take care of
another sick person.

00:04:34.360 --> 00:04:36.220 line:80%
You're spitting all over my face.

00:04:44.480 --> 00:04:45.630 line:80%
Don't worry.

00:04:46.360 --> 00:04:49.290 line:80%
I don't have any
inappropriate thoughts toward you.

00:04:56.480 --> 00:04:58.880 line:80%
Don't blame Mrs. Zhao for meddling either.

00:04:59.650 --> 00:05:00.990 line:80%
She means well.

00:05:04.480 --> 00:05:05.360 line:80%
I know.

00:05:33.770 --> 00:05:34.830 line:80%
What are you doing?

00:05:35.270 --> 00:05:37.060 line:80%
We have to put on a full act.

00:05:38.340 --> 00:05:39.190 line:80%
We

00:05:39.750 --> 00:05:42.810 line:80%
shouldn't let Mr. and Mrs. Zhao
wait outside all night.

00:05:50.600 --> 00:05:51.720 line:80%
It worked.

00:05:53.340 --> 00:05:56.750 line:80%
You said young people
have the desire but not the guts

00:05:57.220 --> 00:05:58.520 line:80%
and older people

00:05:58.520 --> 00:06:00.480 line:80%
have the guts but not the desire.

00:06:00.610 --> 00:06:01.860 line:80%
If you ask me,

00:06:02.120 --> 00:06:06.200 line:80%
there are plenty of young people
with both the desire and the guts.

00:06:07.520 --> 00:06:09.110 line:80%
I just made a passing remark,

00:06:09.110 --> 00:06:11.160 line:80%
and you're rambling on and on.

00:06:12.870 --> 00:06:13.360 line:80%
Wait.

00:06:14.400 --> 00:06:15.750 line:80%
You damn old man.

00:06:16.630 --> 00:06:18.230 line:80%
You heard that by eavesdropping outside.

00:06:18.230 --> 00:06:18.750 line:80%
I...

00:06:19.870 --> 00:06:21.720 line:80%
You're the pot calling the kettle black.

00:06:21.720 --> 00:06:22.960 line:80%
Aren't you eavesdropping too?

00:06:22.960 --> 00:06:24.230 line:80%
I just enjoy this sort of thing.

00:06:24.230 --> 00:06:25.490 line:80%
None of your business!

00:06:35.280 --> 00:06:36.910 line:80%
I only learned of your background

00:06:36.910 --> 00:06:38.540 line:80%
after Mr. Sun came.

00:06:40.280 --> 00:06:42.410 line:80%
You're going to leave sooner or later,

00:06:42.480 --> 00:06:43.140 line:80%
aren't you?

00:06:49.320 --> 00:06:50.580 line:80%
I won't cling to you.

00:06:52.480 --> 00:06:54.550 line:80%
You can leave whenever you want.

00:06:57.070 --> 00:06:58.280 line:80%
For now...

00:06:59.520 --> 00:07:00.480 line:80%
I can't go yet.

00:07:06.360 --> 00:07:07.190 line:80%
That works.

00:07:13.520 --> 00:07:14.780 line:80%
I have something to do.

00:07:16.890 --> 00:07:18.140 line:80%
I have to stay here

00:07:19.090 --> 00:07:19.890 line:80%
to do it.

00:07:26.630 --> 00:07:27.790 line:80%
Let me be on top.

00:07:27.860 --> 00:07:29.020 line:80%
You get some rest.

00:07:36.430 --> 00:07:37.160 line:80%
That works.

00:08:06.980 --> 00:08:09.630 line:80%
There's still a big bowl
of braised meat rice in the kitchen.

00:08:09.630 --> 00:08:11.890 line:80%
If you're hungry, I'll heat it up for you.

00:08:13.230 --> 00:08:14.160 line:80%
I'm not hungry.

00:08:19.910 --> 00:08:22.110 line:80%
I wonder if Changning is sleeping well.

00:08:22.430 --> 00:08:24.760 line:80%
She loves kicking off the covers at night.

00:08:24.950 --> 00:08:26.480 line:80%
I haven't fed the falcon yet either.

00:08:26.480 --> 00:08:27.990 line:80%
If you want to talk,

00:08:30.670 --> 00:08:32.270 line:80%
can I ask you a few questions?

00:08:34.280 --> 00:08:35.040 line:80%
Go ahead.

00:08:37.420 --> 00:08:40.380 line:80%
What kind of people were your parents?

00:08:41.880 --> 00:08:42.609 line:80%
Good people.

00:08:43.830 --> 00:08:45.090 line:80%
How did they treat you?

00:08:46.730 --> 00:08:48.360 line:80%
Just as well as ordinary parents

00:08:48.360 --> 00:08:50.000 line:80%
treat their own children.

00:08:51.880 --> 00:08:53.240 line:80%
If one day,

00:08:54.630 --> 00:08:55.960 line:80%
they wanted to harm you,

00:08:57.600 --> 00:08:58.620 line:80%
what would you do?

00:09:05.590 --> 00:09:08.710 line:80%
When I was little,
my mother used to beat me.

00:09:09.260 --> 00:09:11.320 line:80%
She'd hit my left hand, then my right.

00:09:11.920 --> 00:09:12.670 line:80%
She was heavy-handed.

00:09:12.670 --> 00:09:13.960 line:80%
It really hurt.

00:09:14.120 --> 00:09:15.680 line:80%
But every time she finished,

00:09:15.680 --> 00:09:18.080 line:80%
she'd still buy candy
for Changning and me.

00:09:20.630 --> 00:09:21.760 line:80%
I'm not asking about

00:09:22.560 --> 00:09:24.350 line:80%
such trivial grievances.

00:09:26.780 --> 00:09:27.670 line:80%
I understand.

00:09:29.740 --> 00:09:31.230 line:80%
What I mean is...

00:09:33.300 --> 00:09:34.700 line:80%
People close to you

00:09:35.640 --> 00:09:37.550 line:80%
won't ruthlessly hurt you.

00:09:38.910 --> 00:09:42.750 line:80%
Even if there are arguments or conflicts,

00:09:43.090 --> 00:09:43.980 line:80%
afterwards,

00:09:44.830 --> 00:09:47.490 line:80%
they'll still buy candy
to quietly comfort you.

00:09:51.030 --> 00:09:52.700 line:80%
But if someone

00:09:53.350 --> 00:09:54.950 line:80%
genuinely wants to harm you,

00:09:56.280 --> 00:09:57.740 line:80%
fundamentally speaking,

00:09:58.350 --> 00:10:00.550 line:80%
that person isn't close to you anymore.

00:10:34.620 --> 00:10:36.480 line:80%
Did you eat tangerine peel candy?

00:10:37.210 --> 00:10:39.450 line:80%
You smell like tangerine peel candy.

00:10:39.480 --> 00:10:40.880 line:80%
Did you have a nightmare?

00:10:44.080 --> 00:10:46.390 line:80%
♪ The scenery is as clear as me ♪

00:10:44.810 --> 00:10:46.200 line:80%
Eating candy

00:10:47.280 --> 00:10:48.690 line:80%
helps me sleep.

00:10:47.350 --> 00:10:48.630 line:80%
♪ With very pale colors ♪

00:10:49.500 --> 00:10:52.340 line:80%
♪ Just like the outline in the mirror ♪

00:10:51.190 --> 00:10:53.240 line:80%
If you want more when you return,

00:10:52.770 --> 00:10:55.270 line:80%
♪ I think that's me, being naive ♪

00:10:53.260 --> 00:10:54.270 line:80%
I'll buy you some.

00:10:56.010 --> 00:10:57.660 line:80%
♪ Unlocking my heart ♪

00:10:58.170 --> 00:11:02.420 line:80%
♪ I hid you in my soul ♪

00:10:58.760 --> 00:10:59.850 line:80%
Do you...

00:11:02.310 --> 00:11:03.160 line:80%
want some now?

00:11:05.910 --> 00:11:08.480 line:80%
♪ The moon is as quiet as me ♪

00:11:09.080 --> 00:11:10.760 line:80%
♪ The light shines ♪

00:11:11.500 --> 00:11:14.200 line:80%
♪ It illuminates
the turbulence in my heart ♪

00:11:14.610 --> 00:11:17.330 line:80%
♪ It seems to be the fire of love ♪

00:11:17.810 --> 00:11:19.720 line:80%
♪ Just a few sparks ♪

00:11:20.160 --> 00:11:25.020 line:80%
♪ Let me hide in your heart ♪

00:11:27.340 --> 00:11:28.650 line:80%
♪ I pray that our love ♪

00:11:28.680 --> 00:11:31.300 line:80%
♪ Will never end ♪

00:11:31.980 --> 00:11:32.990 line:80%
♪ It's worth my foolishly waiting ♪

00:11:33.020 --> 00:11:35.320 line:80%
♪ For a lifetime ♪

00:11:35.950 --> 00:11:40.030 line:80%
♪ Clear and quiet as me ♪

00:11:40.500 --> 00:11:44.170 line:80%
♪ So what if we encounter difficulties? ♪

00:11:44.820 --> 00:11:45.800 line:80%
♪ I pray that our love
will not be like sand ♪

00:11:45.820 --> 00:11:48.480 line:80%
♪ Slipping into the sea ♪

00:13:29.120 --> 00:13:31.980 line:80%
What exactly are you looking for
in the Fan's house?

00:13:53.480 --> 00:13:54.430 line:80%
Mr. Li?

00:14:01.330 --> 00:14:02.090 line:80%
Run!

00:14:03.250 --> 00:14:03.850 line:80%
No need.

00:14:06.160 --> 00:14:06.830 line:80%
Seize them!

00:14:15.790 --> 00:14:17.250 line:80%
I'll ask you one more time.

00:14:17.490 --> 00:14:19.550 line:80%
What exactly does the Fan family have

00:14:19.880 --> 00:14:23.340 line:80%
that's worth the Wei family's
Iron Suicide Warriors coming here for?

00:14:23.340 --> 00:14:24.880 line:80%
Who exactly are you?

00:14:25.130 --> 00:14:26.390 line:80%
How do you know who I am?

00:14:32.710 --> 00:14:33.710 line:80%
Marquis of Wu'an?

00:14:34.180 --> 00:14:35.240 line:80%
Why are you here?

00:14:37.600 --> 00:14:39.340 line:80%
I've pried open the mouths

00:14:40.420 --> 00:14:42.440 line:80%
of countless spies in the army.

00:14:43.670 --> 00:14:45.430 line:80%
If you want to try,

00:14:46.840 --> 00:14:48.440 line:80%
I can oblige you.

00:14:49.460 --> 00:14:50.920 line:80%
It was the Prime Minister.

00:14:50.950 --> 00:14:52.410 line:80%
He sent me to find a letter.

00:14:52.410 --> 00:14:53.400 line:80%
What letter?

00:14:59.640 --> 00:15:00.240 line:80%
Speak.

00:15:02.440 --> 00:15:04.640 line:80%
You know the Prime Minister's methods.

00:15:05.190 --> 00:15:07.900 line:80%
Why make things difficult
for a nobody like me?

00:15:08.650 --> 00:15:10.710 line:80%
What else did the Prime Minister say?

00:15:21.640 --> 00:15:22.590 line:80%
Mrs. Fan, are you hurt?

00:15:22.590 --> 00:15:23.430 line:80%
Mr. Li.

00:15:24.770 --> 00:15:25.440 line:80%
I'm sorry.

00:15:27.240 --> 00:15:29.520 line:80%
May I ask your name, My Lord?

00:15:29.880 --> 00:15:32.010 line:80%
I will set up a memorial tablet for you.

00:15:33.430 --> 00:15:35.560 line:80%
It's my duty. There's no need for that.

00:15:39.830 --> 00:15:42.130 line:80%
My lord is
the Martial Commandant of Jizhou,

00:15:42.130 --> 00:15:43.640 line:80%
Li Huaian.

00:15:46.880 --> 00:15:47.960 line:80%
Thank you, Lord Li.

00:15:50.160 --> 00:15:51.080 line:80%
I am humbled.

00:15:51.520 --> 00:15:52.590 line:80%
The rebels are rampant.

00:15:52.590 --> 00:15:53.430 line:80%
After Mr. Mu He of Jizhou

00:15:53.430 --> 00:15:55.280 line:80%
went to guard Lucheng personally,

00:15:55.280 --> 00:15:58.810 line:80%
I was ordered to come here
to assist in suppressing the bandits.

00:15:59.320 --> 00:16:00.980 line:80%
But why were these men in black

00:16:01.260 --> 00:16:02.420 line:80%
hunting you down?

00:16:02.760 --> 00:16:03.890 line:80%
I don't know either.

00:16:07.310 --> 00:16:09.080 line:80%
Oh no. Yan Zheng!

00:16:11.870 --> 00:16:12.530 line:80%
Follow her.

00:16:21.870 --> 00:16:23.130 line:80%
Changyu is back.

00:16:26.830 --> 00:16:27.640 line:80%
Changyu!

00:16:28.470 --> 00:16:30.000 line:80%
Are you and Yan Zheng hurt?

00:16:30.000 --> 00:16:31.670 line:80%
What's with the dead bodies at the door?

00:16:31.670 --> 00:16:32.270 line:80%
I'm fine.

00:16:32.350 --> 00:16:33.760 line:80%
Mrs. Zhao, please look after Changning.

00:16:33.760 --> 00:16:33.950 line:80%
Okay.

00:16:33.950 --> 00:16:35.310 line:80%
Don't let her get scared.

00:16:35.310 --> 00:16:36.310 line:80%
Go inside, quick.

00:16:36.430 --> 00:16:37.120 line:80%
Quickly.

00:16:37.760 --> 00:16:38.620 line:80%
Don't come out.

00:16:38.800 --> 00:16:39.660 line:80%
My Lord, you...

00:16:42.830 --> 00:16:45.350 line:80%
You're that gentleman from last time?

00:16:45.470 --> 00:16:47.760 line:80%
I was sent by the Jizhou Prefecture
to investigate the case.

00:16:47.760 --> 00:16:50.310 line:80%
My Lord, you must investigate thoroughly.

00:16:50.310 --> 00:16:52.160 line:80%
The Fan family is so unlucky.

00:16:52.160 --> 00:16:52.950 line:80%
Yes.

00:16:58.240 --> 00:16:58.950 line:80%
Yan Zheng!

00:17:02.350 --> 00:17:03.040 line:80%
Move!

00:17:03.310 --> 00:17:04.040 line:80%
Yan Zheng.

00:17:04.240 --> 00:17:05.040 line:80%
Yan Zheng.

00:17:05.110 --> 00:17:06.240 line:80%
Yan Zheng, wake up!

00:17:06.800 --> 00:17:07.480 line:80%
Get up.

00:17:08.000 --> 00:17:08.629 line:80%
Get up.

00:17:11.629 --> 00:17:12.889 line:80%
-Yan Zheng!
-Changyu!

00:17:12.909 --> 00:17:13.629 line:80%
Changyu!

00:17:15.090 --> 00:17:15.830 line:80%
Mr. Zhao,

00:17:16.000 --> 00:17:17.200 line:80%
come and check on him.

00:17:17.480 --> 00:17:18.340 line:80%
Don't move him.

00:17:18.550 --> 00:17:20.750 line:80%
Don't make the injuries worse.

00:17:21.440 --> 00:17:23.280 line:80%
Let me take a look.

00:17:27.590 --> 00:17:28.720 line:80%
Yan Zheng, wake up.

00:17:29.480 --> 00:17:30.280 line:80%
Yan Zheng.

00:17:49.310 --> 00:17:50.240 line:80%
Did your husband

00:17:50.260 --> 00:17:51.640 line:80%
kill this one

00:17:51.910 --> 00:17:53.710 line:80%
and the men in black downstairs?

00:17:56.480 --> 00:17:58.540 line:80%
My husband used to be an armed escort.

00:17:58.640 --> 00:18:00.640 line:80%
He's quite skilled in martial arts.

00:18:01.140 --> 00:18:02.110 line:80%
Officer,

00:18:02.280 --> 00:18:04.410 line:80%
you must uphold justice for us.

00:18:04.680 --> 00:18:06.650 line:80%
This girl has a hard life.

00:18:06.760 --> 00:18:08.710 line:80%
Her parents just passed away last month.

00:18:08.710 --> 00:18:11.390 line:80%
She finally found a husband
to marry into the family.

00:18:11.390 --> 00:18:12.560 line:80%
But now,

00:18:12.630 --> 00:18:14.930 line:80%
he's been injured by these thugs too.

00:18:15.110 --> 00:18:17.870 line:80%
If we can't find out
where these criminals came from,

00:18:17.870 --> 00:18:20.440 line:80%
how will she survive in the future?

00:18:20.460 --> 00:18:22.310 line:80%
My Lord!

00:18:22.720 --> 00:18:24.980 line:80%
My Lord, there's a survivor downstairs.

00:18:25.690 --> 00:18:26.400 line:80%
Don't worry.

00:18:26.400 --> 00:18:26.910 line:80%
Okay.

00:18:30.230 --> 00:18:32.220 line:80%
Mr. Zhao, take another look.

00:18:32.590 --> 00:18:33.680 line:80%
Let me check again.

00:18:33.720 --> 00:18:35.470 line:80%
Let me check again.

00:18:36.310 --> 00:18:39.100 line:80%
My Lord, this matrilocal husband
is very suspicious.

00:18:39.100 --> 00:18:40.590 line:80%
Shouldn't we take him back
for questioning?

00:18:40.590 --> 00:18:42.340 line:80%
No rush. I know what I'm doing.

00:18:42.440 --> 00:18:44.000 line:80%
Let's go check on that survivor first.

00:18:44.000 --> 00:18:44.310 line:80%
Yes,

00:18:44.310 --> 00:18:44.870 line:80%
My Lord.

00:18:48.520 --> 00:18:49.390 line:80%
If I had known,

00:18:50.310 --> 00:18:52.510 line:80%
I would have written the divorce papers

00:18:53.170 --> 00:18:55.170 line:80%
and let you recover somewhere else.

00:18:56.280 --> 00:18:58.680 line:80%
Then you wouldn't have to
suffer like this.

00:19:03.680 --> 00:19:08.550 line:80%
I was ordered to kill
the Fan family's daughter

00:19:08.550 --> 00:19:10.570 line:80%
and retrieve the letter.

00:19:10.870 --> 00:19:12.010 line:80%
The letter?

00:19:21.110 --> 00:19:22.220 line:80%
Fan Changyu!

00:20:17.680 --> 00:20:20.280 line:80%
He's covered in blood

00:20:20.520 --> 00:20:23.030 line:80%
and looks like he's badly hurt,

00:20:23.830 --> 00:20:26.910 line:80%
but his pulse isn't weak at all.

00:20:27.800 --> 00:20:29.440 line:80%
But he's lost so much blood.

00:20:33.240 --> 00:20:34.400 line:80%
Strange.

00:20:35.040 --> 00:20:36.960 line:80%
There are no new wounds.

00:20:37.550 --> 00:20:38.480 line:80%
This blood

00:20:39.040 --> 00:20:41.350 line:80%
is from old wounds reopening.

00:20:42.440 --> 00:20:44.300 line:80%
Let me check the wound on his back.

00:20:45.550 --> 00:20:46.350 line:80%
You're awake.

00:20:47.410 --> 00:20:48.860 line:80%
Yan Zheng, you're awake?

00:20:52.260 --> 00:21:02.310 line:80%
♪ In gold-thread dress,
with moth or willow ornaments ♪

00:20:56.240 --> 00:20:57.460 line:80%
I'm fine.

00:20:58.190 --> 00:20:59.800 line:80%
It's all blood from other people.

00:20:59.800 --> 00:21:01.070 line:80%
Help him onto the bed.

00:21:02.520 --> 00:21:03.390 line:80%
Careful, careful.

00:21:03.170 --> 00:21:12.700 line:80%
♪ Giggling, she melts into the throng
with trails of scents ♪

00:21:03.960 --> 00:21:05.390 line:80%
Slowly, slowly.

00:21:11.870 --> 00:21:13.130 line:80%
As long as you're okay.

00:21:13.770 --> 00:21:18.300 line:80%
♪ But in the crowd once and again
I look for her in vain ♪

00:21:14.220 --> 00:21:15.480 line:80%
As long as you're okay.

00:21:18.320 --> 00:21:23.310 line:80%
♪ But in the crowd once and again
I look for her in vain ♪

00:21:23.860 --> 00:21:25.980 line:80%
♪ When all at once I turn my head ♪

00:21:26.570 --> 00:21:29.370 line:80%
♪ I find her there ♪

00:21:29.040 --> 00:21:30.000 line:80%
Yan Zheng!

00:21:30.050 --> 00:21:34.490 line:80%
♪ Where lantern light is dimly shed ♪

00:21:33.840 --> 00:21:36.280 line:80%
Don't worry. I'm okay.

00:21:35.350 --> 00:21:39.880 line:80%
♪ But in the crowd once and again
I look for her in vain ♪

00:21:39.900 --> 00:21:44.890 line:80%
♪ But in the crowd once and again
I look for her in vain ♪

00:21:42.870 --> 00:21:45.800 line:80%
Changyu, the soldiers need a statement.

00:21:45.650 --> 00:21:47.660 line:80%
♪ When all at once I turn my head ♪

00:21:48.150 --> 00:21:52.530 line:80%
♪ I find her there ♪

00:21:49.020 --> 00:21:49.730 line:80%
Go ahead.

00:21:53.040 --> 00:21:54.240 line:80%
Take care of yourself.

00:21:54.240 --> 00:22:04.160 line:80%
♪ Where lantern light is dimly shed ♪

00:22:04.250 --> 00:22:05.060 line:80%
[Travel Permit]

00:22:05.060 --> 00:22:06.160 line:80%
[Yan of Yan Village,
Changle County, Xuzhou]

00:22:06.180 --> 00:22:07.180 line:80%
[This is a formal report]

00:22:07.210 --> 00:22:08.510 line:80%
[While escorting a convoy to Chongzhou,
he encountered bandits]

00:22:08.530 --> 00:22:09.940 line:80%
[and was stranded in
Lin'an Town, Qingping County, Suzhou]

00:22:14.760 --> 00:22:15.680 line:80%
Changyu.

00:22:16.870 --> 00:22:19.110 line:80%
What does the Martial Commandant do?

00:22:21.100 --> 00:22:22.980 line:80%
Mrs. Zhao, my surname is Li.

00:22:23.910 --> 00:22:24.760 line:80%
Lord Li.

00:22:24.960 --> 00:22:25.870 line:80%
Lord Li.

00:22:27.150 --> 00:22:28.630 line:80%
Before, I thought

00:22:28.630 --> 00:22:30.440 line:80%
you were just a frail scholar.

00:22:30.760 --> 00:22:33.690 line:80%
I didn't expect you to be
a high official from Jizhou.

00:22:33.800 --> 00:22:35.240 line:80%
Since I've come this time,

00:22:35.240 --> 00:22:37.310 line:80%
I will definitely
identify all the criminals

00:22:37.310 --> 00:22:39.110 line:80%
and bring justice to the people.

00:22:45.530 --> 00:22:46.150 line:80%
The survivor

00:22:46.150 --> 00:22:48.350 line:80%
has been taken back for interrogation.

00:22:49.480 --> 00:22:50.940 line:80%
Just wait at home for news.

00:22:51.070 --> 00:22:52.310 line:80%
Once the case is resolved,

00:22:52.310 --> 00:22:54.170 line:80%
the authorities will inform you.

00:22:54.440 --> 00:22:55.200 line:80%
Lord Li,

00:22:55.480 --> 00:22:56.830 line:80%
if those people come back for revenge,

00:22:56.830 --> 00:22:57.870 line:80%
what should we do?

00:22:58.070 --> 00:23:00.600 line:80%
I know I shouldn't
ask too much about the case,

00:23:00.680 --> 00:23:02.280 line:80%
but my sister is still young.

00:23:03.440 --> 00:23:04.720 line:80%
I was thinking

00:23:04.740 --> 00:23:07.140 line:80%
we could leave after the New Year
to lie low.

00:23:08.130 --> 00:23:09.530 line:80%
You want to leave Lin'an?

00:23:14.520 --> 00:23:16.120 line:80%
Is this your husband's idea?

00:23:16.630 --> 00:23:17.440 line:80%
It's my idea.

00:23:17.590 --> 00:23:19.250 line:80%
I'm the head of the household.

00:23:20.630 --> 00:23:21.590 line:80%
I want to leave

00:23:22.760 --> 00:23:26.020 line:80%
because I fear something like tonight
might happen again.

00:23:26.830 --> 00:23:29.040 line:80%
Your parents and uncle
were killed one after another.

00:23:29.040 --> 00:23:30.150 line:80%
Although you are the victim,

00:23:30.150 --> 00:23:31.220 line:80%
you are also a witness.

00:23:31.220 --> 00:23:32.790 line:80%
Until the case is solved,

00:23:33.040 --> 00:23:34.440 line:80%
you cannot leave Lin'an.

00:23:36.440 --> 00:23:37.350 line:80%
But rest assured.

00:23:37.350 --> 00:23:39.200 line:80%
I will station
enough soldiers in the village.

00:23:39.200 --> 00:23:40.930 line:80%
Naturally, we will protect you

00:23:40.970 --> 00:23:43.230 line:80%
and your family until the case is solved.

00:23:43.970 --> 00:23:45.950 line:80%
Lord Li, you are truly a saint.

00:23:46.070 --> 00:23:48.070 line:80%
We are relieved to hear you say that.

00:23:48.520 --> 00:23:51.220 line:80%
Search every house! Quickly!

00:23:52.000 --> 00:23:53.240 line:80%
Within this county,

00:23:53.550 --> 00:23:57.380 line:80%
I will absolutely not allow anyone
to harm the innocent.

00:23:57.550 --> 00:24:00.310 line:80%
I will definitely
give the people an answer today.

00:24:00.310 --> 00:24:01.630 line:80%
Search carefully!

00:24:02.240 --> 00:24:04.150 line:80%
Don't let a single criminal escape!

00:24:04.150 --> 00:24:04.830 line:80%
-Yes!
-Yes!

00:24:10.680 --> 00:24:11.390 line:80%
Lord Li.

00:24:14.000 --> 00:24:15.710 line:80%
Greetings, Lord Li.

00:24:17.030 --> 00:24:19.780 line:80%
I heard criminals were causing trouble
in Xigu Lane,

00:24:19.780 --> 00:24:21.800 line:80%
so I personally led men to take them down.

00:24:21.800 --> 00:24:23.590 line:80%
I didn't expect to meet you here, Lord Li.

00:24:23.590 --> 00:24:24.460 line:80%
Please forgive me

00:24:24.460 --> 00:24:26.120 line:80%
for not welcoming you sooner.

00:24:26.960 --> 00:24:27.590 line:80%
My Lord!

00:24:28.630 --> 00:24:29.440 line:80%
My Lord!

00:24:32.070 --> 00:24:32.760 line:80%
My Lord.

00:24:33.830 --> 00:24:36.870 line:80%
I found a memorial tablet for
the Marquis of Wu'an in this courtyard.

00:24:36.870 --> 00:24:38.070 line:80%
Please look, My Lord.

00:24:38.950 --> 00:24:40.740 line:80%
How dare they

00:24:40.760 --> 00:24:43.040 line:80%
privately mourn the Marquis of Wu'an?

00:24:43.380 --> 00:24:44.250 line:80%
Look, My Lord.

00:24:46.370 --> 00:24:48.220 line:80%
[Xie Zheng, Marquis of Wu'an]

00:24:48.680 --> 00:24:49.280 line:80%
Who is it?

00:24:49.720 --> 00:24:51.040 line:80%
Whose house is this?

00:24:52.760 --> 00:24:55.110 line:80%
My Lord, this is my house.

00:24:55.870 --> 00:24:56.390 line:80%
You?

00:24:57.110 --> 00:24:58.550 line:80%
Fan Changyu?

00:24:58.910 --> 00:24:59.960 line:80%
You again?

00:24:59.980 --> 00:25:01.250 line:80%
My Lord,

00:25:01.590 --> 00:25:03.430 line:80%
does the Legal Code of Great Yin state

00:25:03.430 --> 00:25:05.800 line:80%
that paying respects to
the Marquis of Wu'an is forbidden?

00:25:05.800 --> 00:25:06.880 line:80%
You plebeian,

00:25:06.910 --> 00:25:08.340 line:80%
how dare you talk back?

00:25:08.450 --> 00:25:10.360 line:80%
Men, tie her up and take her back.

00:25:10.480 --> 00:25:11.910 line:80%
Take the memorial tablet too.

00:25:11.910 --> 00:25:14.300 line:80%
You're caught red-handed this time.

00:25:14.390 --> 00:25:15.970 line:80%
Why am I not aware

00:25:15.990 --> 00:25:17.480 line:80%
that the Imperial Court forbids
paying respects to the Marquis of Wu'an?

00:25:17.480 --> 00:25:18.240 line:80%
Well...

00:25:20.300 --> 00:25:22.570 line:80%
My Lord, you are a top scholar.

00:25:22.590 --> 00:25:23.450 line:80%
Surely you know

00:25:23.480 --> 00:25:27.480 line:80%
that the Marquis of Wu'an's evil deeds
are despised by civil officials?

00:25:29.200 --> 00:25:31.590 line:80%
I also heard
that about him massacring a city,

00:25:31.590 --> 00:25:33.070 line:80%
Grand Tutor Li...

00:25:33.070 --> 00:25:34.680 line:80%
The Marquis of Wu'an's
past merits and faults

00:25:34.680 --> 00:25:36.810 line:80%
will be judged by future generations.

00:25:37.310 --> 00:25:38.770 line:80%
He fought for the country.

00:25:39.140 --> 00:25:40.350 line:80%
He died honorably.

00:25:46.630 --> 00:25:48.040 line:80%
Well...

00:25:49.870 --> 00:25:51.930 line:80%
Paying respects to him is not a crime.

00:25:57.390 --> 00:25:58.450 line:80%
Thank you, My Lord.

00:26:02.590 --> 00:26:05.410 line:80%
My Lord, you truly enlightened me.

00:26:06.000 --> 00:26:07.820 line:80%
I was too narrow-minded.

00:26:08.600 --> 00:26:09.800 line:80%
In that case,

00:26:09.830 --> 00:26:11.440 line:80%
Lord Li, please return to town first

00:26:11.440 --> 00:26:13.150 line:80%
so I can report on the case.

00:26:13.170 --> 00:26:14.230 line:80%
After you, My Lord.

00:26:14.440 --> 00:26:15.110 line:80%
Please.

00:26:17.000 --> 00:26:18.210 line:80%
Please.

00:26:25.600 --> 00:26:28.750 line:80%
[Northwest Inn]

00:26:29.630 --> 00:26:30.760 line:80%
Watch out, My Lord.

00:26:31.040 --> 00:26:32.070 line:80%
Mind the steps.

00:26:38.040 --> 00:26:39.110 line:80%
General, please stay.

00:26:39.110 --> 00:26:40.240 line:80%
No need to see me off.

00:26:40.390 --> 00:26:41.070 line:80%
Take care, My Lord.

00:26:41.070 --> 00:26:43.000 line:80%
Forgive me for not walking you out.

00:26:48.870 --> 00:26:51.010 line:80%
Say, this Li Huaian

00:26:51.200 --> 00:26:53.460 line:80%
was expressionless the whole time.

00:26:54.100 --> 00:26:54.970 line:80%
Why is that?

00:26:55.790 --> 00:26:58.230 line:80%
Grand Tutor Li's faction
and Prime Minister Wei's faction

00:26:58.230 --> 00:26:59.590 line:80%
have always been at odds.

00:26:59.590 --> 00:27:01.570 line:80%
Every official in the court knows it.

00:27:01.570 --> 00:27:03.150 line:80%
But when it comes to Lord Li,

00:27:03.150 --> 00:27:05.410 line:80%
why did he speak up for
the Marquis of Wu'an?

00:27:03.210 --> 00:27:06.180 line:80%
[Northwest Inn]

00:27:05.520 --> 00:27:06.490 line:80%
Exactly.

00:27:07.760 --> 00:27:08.620 line:80%
Think about it.

00:27:09.150 --> 00:27:11.350 line:80%
If they've always been enemies,

00:27:12.110 --> 00:27:13.830 line:80%
then why would Grand Tutor Li

00:27:14.000 --> 00:27:15.880 line:80%
let his eldest grandson

00:27:15.940 --> 00:27:18.340 line:80%
study under He Jingyuan
of the Wei faction?

00:27:19.960 --> 00:27:20.870 line:80%
Is that so?

00:27:21.740 --> 00:27:24.210 line:80%
Could there be a past connection?

00:27:28.040 --> 00:27:31.300 line:80%
Who can guess what these
powerful officials are thinking?

00:27:33.520 --> 00:27:34.590 line:80%
I am

00:27:34.960 --> 00:27:36.640 line:80%
stuck in this backwater town.

00:27:36.880 --> 00:27:38.590 line:80%
Even if the court farts,

00:27:38.640 --> 00:27:41.240 line:80%
the stink is gone
by the time it reaches Lin'an.

00:27:42.310 --> 00:27:43.280 line:80%
I say,

00:27:43.480 --> 00:27:44.590 line:80%
this mess is all your fault.

00:27:44.590 --> 00:27:45.850 line:80%
You gave me bad advice.

00:27:45.910 --> 00:27:47.720 line:80%
I tried to flatter him
and got on his bad side instead.

00:27:47.720 --> 00:27:48.710 line:80%
Yes, yes.

00:27:49.200 --> 00:27:50.070 line:80%
It's my fault.

00:27:50.150 --> 00:27:50.680 line:80%
It's all my fault.

00:27:50.680 --> 00:27:51.610 line:80%
Enough, enough.

00:27:51.960 --> 00:27:53.890 line:80%
Let's go back and rethink our plan.

00:27:56.310 --> 00:27:59.040 line:80%
Finally got rid of
that bootlicking magistrate.

00:27:59.870 --> 00:28:00.440 line:80%
My Lord.

00:28:01.200 --> 00:28:02.150 line:80%
We found that

00:28:02.240 --> 00:28:05.040 line:80%
these assassins
all carried a black iron whistle.

00:28:09.150 --> 00:28:10.480 line:80%
Black iron whistles...

00:28:10.720 --> 00:28:11.580 line:80%
The capital...

00:28:12.410 --> 00:28:14.470 line:80%
Committing suicide upon failure...

00:28:16.760 --> 00:28:17.720 line:80%
It does resemble

00:28:17.720 --> 00:28:20.920 line:80%
the style of the Wei faction's
rumored Suicide Warriors.

00:28:21.550 --> 00:28:22.810 line:80%
Who would have thought

00:28:23.850 --> 00:28:27.110 line:80%
that the Marquis of Wu'an we searched for
on the front lines

00:28:27.790 --> 00:28:29.990 line:80%
became a matrilocal husband in Lin'an?

00:28:30.830 --> 00:28:31.470 line:80%
Who?

00:28:32.120 --> 00:28:33.580 line:80%
He is the Marquis of Wu'an?

00:28:33.600 --> 00:28:34.730 line:80%
That's impossible.

00:28:35.170 --> 00:28:37.630 line:80%
The Marquis of Wu'an
has such a fiery temper.

00:28:37.680 --> 00:28:39.260 line:80%
Never mind that he's in trouble now,

00:28:39.260 --> 00:28:41.600 line:80%
but even if His Majesty
threw him in the Imperial Prison

00:28:41.600 --> 00:28:43.970 line:80%
to force him to marry the Eldest Princess
and join the imperial family,

00:28:43.970 --> 00:28:45.370 line:80%
he still wouldn't agree.

00:28:45.400 --> 00:28:47.200 line:80%
When we were young,

00:28:47.720 --> 00:28:51.320 line:80%
we studied martial arts
and strategy together with our teacher.

00:28:51.390 --> 00:28:52.480 line:80%
Though we haven't met in over a decade,

00:28:52.480 --> 00:28:54.280 line:80%
and his appearance has changed,

00:28:54.890 --> 00:28:56.360 line:80%
I am 60 percent sure

00:28:57.150 --> 00:28:58.010 line:80%
that it was him.

00:28:59.680 --> 00:29:01.080 line:80%
Whether it was him or not,

00:29:01.590 --> 00:29:03.250 line:80%
deliver this quickly Yanzhou

00:29:03.530 --> 00:29:04.470 line:80%
and we will know.

00:29:07.730 --> 00:29:10.050 line:80%
[Xigu Lane]

00:29:13.680 --> 00:29:14.720 line:80%
That's all.

00:29:15.310 --> 00:29:17.360 line:80%
The harvest is bad this year.

00:29:17.390 --> 00:29:19.120 line:80%
It's the same for every family.

00:29:25.840 --> 00:29:27.350 line:80%
Have you heard?

00:29:27.480 --> 00:29:29.540 line:80%
People died at the Fan's house again.

00:29:30.380 --> 00:29:31.690 line:80%
After Fan Erniu and his wife

00:29:31.690 --> 00:29:33.630 line:80%
died because of Changyu's bad luck,

00:29:33.630 --> 00:29:35.490 line:80%
their family hasn't known peace.

00:29:36.550 --> 00:29:39.590 line:80%
I heard her matrilocal husband
was badly hurt.

00:29:39.630 --> 00:29:42.440 line:80%
Who knows if he can still
perform as a man.

00:29:44.150 --> 00:29:45.150 line:80%
That Fan Changyu

00:29:45.200 --> 00:29:46.590 line:80%
is a jinx.

00:29:46.780 --> 00:29:48.110 line:80%
Scholar Song

00:29:48.110 --> 00:29:49.760 line:80%
was lucky to break off the engagement.

00:29:49.760 --> 00:29:50.960 line:80%
He escaped disaster.

00:29:51.070 --> 00:29:52.110 line:80%
Scholar Song

00:29:52.110 --> 00:29:54.850 line:80%
is the Star of Wisdom incarnate.
He's blessed.

00:29:55.010 --> 00:29:55.660 line:80%
Yes.

00:29:57.020 --> 00:29:57.670 line:80%
Yes.

00:30:03.040 --> 00:30:03.950 line:80%
Who is that?

00:30:04.690 --> 00:30:05.460 line:80%
I don't know.

00:30:10.070 --> 00:30:11.700 line:80%
What do you want?

00:30:11.720 --> 00:30:13.140 line:80%
We should be asking you.

00:30:13.520 --> 00:30:14.580 line:80%
Where are you from?

00:30:14.680 --> 00:30:16.210 line:80%
Why are you eavesdropping?

00:30:17.210 --> 00:30:18.870 line:80%
We are from Jizhou Prefecture.

00:30:18.870 --> 00:30:19.990 line:80%
We are old friends of the Fan family.

00:30:19.990 --> 00:30:21.390 line:80%
Hearing news about them,

00:30:21.960 --> 00:30:23.890 line:80%
we couldn't help but be concerned.

00:30:24.520 --> 00:30:27.730 line:80%
Strangers prying
right after the Fan family incident?

00:30:27.860 --> 00:30:29.840 line:80%
They must be up to no good.

00:30:29.960 --> 00:30:32.490 line:80%
I say we report
to the officials immediately.

00:30:32.760 --> 00:30:35.820 line:80%
Judging by his looks,
he doesn't seem like a bad person.

00:30:35.830 --> 00:30:38.230 line:80%
Villains don't have labels on their faces.

00:30:38.440 --> 00:30:39.800 line:80%
I certainly won't

00:30:40.040 --> 00:30:42.040 line:80%
waste everyone's time for nothing.

00:30:49.760 --> 00:30:50.520 line:80%
Let me tell you.

00:30:50.520 --> 00:30:51.440 line:80%
I know.

00:30:52.610 --> 00:30:53.900 line:80%
I'll talk.

00:30:54.910 --> 00:30:56.520 line:80%
Martial Commandant!

00:30:58.070 --> 00:30:59.240 line:80%
Hello.

00:30:59.490 --> 00:31:00.870 line:80%
You're still in the village?

00:31:00.870 --> 00:31:01.800 line:80%
You haven't left yet?

00:31:01.800 --> 00:31:02.330 line:80%
Yes, yes.

00:31:03.200 --> 00:31:04.310 line:80%
What's going on?

00:31:05.280 --> 00:31:07.180 line:80%
What... Who is this?

00:31:07.590 --> 00:31:10.070 line:80%
He's a big official from Jizhou
to investigate the case.

00:31:10.070 --> 00:31:11.040 line:80%
A big official?

00:31:11.200 --> 00:31:12.940 line:80%
I still have some questions.

00:31:15.480 --> 00:31:16.480 line:80%
I don't know them well!

00:31:16.480 --> 00:31:17.200 line:80%
Take it back.

00:31:17.200 --> 00:31:18.350 line:80%
We haven't asked yet!

00:31:18.350 --> 00:31:18.760 line:80%
Honestly.

00:31:18.760 --> 00:31:19.590 line:80%
Mrs. Zhao.

00:31:19.870 --> 00:31:20.390 line:80%
Sir,

00:31:21.010 --> 00:31:22.330 line:80%
do you still want this?

00:31:26.110 --> 00:31:26.960 line:80%
Zhao.

00:31:26.980 --> 00:31:27.920 line:80%
Zhao.

00:31:28.150 --> 00:31:29.000 line:80%
That...

00:31:29.590 --> 00:31:31.680 line:80%
What does that Commandant guy do?

00:31:33.110 --> 00:31:34.150 line:80%
I don't know.

00:31:34.240 --> 00:31:36.720 line:80%
But even the magistrate is polite to them.

00:31:39.550 --> 00:31:40.280 line:80%
Ladies.

00:31:41.130 --> 00:31:41.910 line:80%
Don't ask us.

00:31:41.910 --> 00:31:42.520 line:80%
We don't know.

00:31:42.520 --> 00:31:43.310 line:80%
We're not close to the Fan family.

00:31:43.310 --> 00:31:43.910 line:80%
Not close.

00:31:43.980 --> 00:31:45.040 line:80%
Just one question!

00:32:06.280 --> 00:32:08.210 line:80%
Sir, I'd like to ask...

00:32:08.240 --> 00:32:09.960 line:80%
I don't know.

00:32:16.830 --> 00:32:18.680 line:80%
My Lord, I didn't find out much.

00:32:18.960 --> 00:32:20.360 line:80%
No one is willing to talk.

00:32:20.520 --> 00:32:22.870 line:80%
I only know Mrs. Fan
wanted to keep her property,

00:32:22.870 --> 00:32:24.910 line:80%
so she took in an outsider
named Yan Zheng as a husband.

00:32:24.910 --> 00:32:26.310 line:80%
He was injured by bandits

00:32:26.310 --> 00:32:27.510 line:80%
and saved by Mrs. Fan.

00:32:27.760 --> 00:32:29.960 line:80%
Based on the travel permits we checked,

00:32:30.520 --> 00:32:32.180 line:80%
there's nothing suspicious.

00:32:32.390 --> 00:32:34.650 line:80%
If the Marquis of Wu'an planned all this,

00:32:34.960 --> 00:32:36.890 line:80%
we certainly won't find anything.

00:32:37.440 --> 00:32:39.300 line:80%
Why not ask the Zhao family again?

00:32:39.480 --> 00:32:41.040 line:80%
Mrs. Zhao looks shrewd,

00:32:41.110 --> 00:32:43.170 line:80%
but her husband seems easy to talk to.

00:32:43.870 --> 00:32:46.000 line:80%
Given their relationship with Changyu,

00:32:46.000 --> 00:32:47.680 line:80%
their testimony might be biased.

00:32:47.680 --> 00:32:48.280 line:80%
True.

00:32:53.590 --> 00:32:54.390 line:80%
My Lord.

00:32:59.910 --> 00:33:02.630 line:80%
You want to know about the Fan family?

00:33:04.800 --> 00:33:06.610 line:80%
I actually know quite a lot.

00:33:07.550 --> 00:33:08.800 line:80%
It's just that...

00:33:16.350 --> 00:33:17.070 line:80%
My Lord,

00:33:17.390 --> 00:33:18.480 line:80%
that Fan Changyu

00:33:18.480 --> 00:33:20.130 line:80%
is cursed.

00:33:20.150 --> 00:33:22.200 line:80%
She didn't just curse
her parents to death.

00:33:22.200 --> 00:33:24.130 line:80%
She even cursed her uncle to death.

00:33:24.870 --> 00:33:27.640 line:80%
And that husband of hers

00:33:27.680 --> 00:33:29.000 line:80%
is quite handsome,

00:33:29.420 --> 00:33:32.560 line:80%
but he has no backbone at all.

00:33:33.070 --> 00:33:34.290 line:80%
During the wedding ceremony,

00:33:34.290 --> 00:33:37.330 line:80%
he actually swore
to obey Fan Changyu in everything.

00:33:37.440 --> 00:33:39.130 line:80%
He just lives off her.

00:33:39.390 --> 00:33:43.120 line:80%
You mean he publicly acknowledged Mrs. Fan
as the head of the house?

00:33:43.910 --> 00:33:45.800 line:80%
All the villagers saw and heard it.

00:33:45.800 --> 00:33:47.870 line:80%
I'm not making this up.

00:33:51.350 --> 00:33:51.960 line:80%
My Lord,

00:33:52.310 --> 00:33:53.970 line:80%
I'll tell you another secret.

00:33:55.160 --> 00:33:56.470 line:80%
That Fan Changyu

00:33:56.530 --> 00:33:59.930 line:80%
and her matrilocal husband
are likely just putting on a show.

00:34:00.280 --> 00:34:01.940 line:80%
They haven't shared a bed yet.

00:34:02.480 --> 00:34:05.350 line:80%
Fan Changyu is still a virgin.

00:34:06.870 --> 00:34:08.410 line:80%
Watch your filthy tongue.

00:34:08.439 --> 00:34:10.039 line:80%
Do not defile My Lord's ears.

00:34:10.430 --> 00:34:11.030 line:80%
It's fine.

00:34:11.950 --> 00:34:12.760 line:80%
Let her speak.

00:34:12.910 --> 00:34:15.170 line:80%
What's there to be ashamed of?

00:34:15.310 --> 00:34:17.340 line:80%
Her brows are still tight

00:34:17.640 --> 00:34:18.760 line:80%
and her steps are light.

00:34:18.760 --> 00:34:20.390 line:80%
If that doesn't make her a virgin,

00:34:20.390 --> 00:34:21.499 line:80%
then what is she?

00:34:21.680 --> 00:34:22.410 line:80%
Understood.

00:34:22.459 --> 00:34:23.620 line:80%
We've heard enough.

00:34:23.840 --> 00:34:25.570 line:80%
Thank you for the information.

00:34:26.950 --> 00:34:27.880 line:80%
My Lord, My Lord!

00:34:30.310 --> 00:34:32.019 line:80%
You must not tell anyone

00:34:32.050 --> 00:34:34.090 line:80%
that I was the one who told you.

00:34:34.200 --> 00:34:35.340 line:80%
You know,

00:34:35.360 --> 00:34:37.689 line:80%
Fan Changyu used to be a butcher.

00:34:37.720 --> 00:34:39.180 line:80%
She has immense strength.

00:34:39.180 --> 00:34:40.380 line:80%
I've experienced it.

00:34:42.170 --> 00:34:42.760 line:80%
My Lord.

00:34:42.760 --> 00:34:43.280 line:80%
All right, enough.

00:34:43.280 --> 00:34:45.080 line:80%
-I have more.
-Thank you, madam.

00:34:45.720 --> 00:34:46.430 line:80%
Stop following us.

00:34:46.430 --> 00:34:48.080 line:80%
I haven't finished yet!

00:34:50.310 --> 00:34:51.470 line:80%
How could the dignified Marquis of Wu'an

00:34:51.470 --> 00:34:52.990 line:80%
publicly acknowledge a woman as his master

00:34:52.990 --> 00:34:54.390 line:80%
and become a matrilocal husband?

00:34:54.390 --> 00:34:56.560 line:80%
My Lord, how certain are you now?

00:34:58.180 --> 00:34:59.180 line:80%
Seventy percent.

00:35:01.640 --> 00:35:02.640 line:80%
Seventy percent?

00:35:02.780 --> 00:35:04.160 line:80%
How come it went up?

00:35:04.590 --> 00:35:07.910 line:80%
[Changzhou Magistrate]

00:35:06.720 --> 00:35:09.240 line:80%
The terrain east of Chongzhou
is precipitous.

00:35:09.240 --> 00:35:09.990 line:80%
Easy to defend and hard to attack,

00:35:09.990 --> 00:35:11.450 line:80%
it is a natural barrier.

00:35:11.220 --> 00:35:13.940 line:80%
[Magistrate]

00:35:11.680 --> 00:35:13.310 line:80%
If the enemy holds their ground here,

00:35:13.310 --> 00:35:14.430 line:80%
our army will struggle to cross.

00:35:14.010 --> 00:35:18.740 line:80%
[The world is benevolent]

00:35:15.160 --> 00:35:15.910 line:80%
General,

00:35:15.910 --> 00:35:18.470 line:80%
perhaps we can go through
Mount Heng's ravine

00:35:18.470 --> 00:35:19.850 line:80%
to launch a flanking maneuver.

00:35:19.850 --> 00:35:23.390 line:80%
[He Jingyuan, Prefect of Jizhou]

00:35:19.990 --> 00:35:21.720 line:80%
We can bypass their front defense line

00:35:21.720 --> 00:35:23.980 line:80%
and attack their flank or rear directly.

00:35:32.990 --> 00:35:34.990 line:80%
Why is the magistrate's open office

00:35:35.110 --> 00:35:36.970 line:80%
closed so tightly during the day?

00:35:37.510 --> 00:35:38.600 line:80%
Or does

00:35:37.770 --> 00:35:41.540 line:80%
[Wei Xuan, son of Wei Yan]

00:35:39.080 --> 00:35:41.510 line:80%
General He have some unspeakable secret?

00:35:45.600 --> 00:35:48.200 line:80%
Why did that rascal Li Huaian
go to Lin'an Town?

00:35:49.240 --> 00:35:50.640 line:80%
Is Old Man Li

00:35:51.330 --> 00:35:53.060 line:80%
targeting my Wei family again?

00:35:54.870 --> 00:35:57.470 line:80%
Bandits are rampant around Lin'an.

00:35:58.080 --> 00:35:59.610 line:80%
I sent him to suppress them.

00:35:59.870 --> 00:36:02.470 line:80%
He encountered a murder case in town,

00:36:02.640 --> 00:36:04.310 line:80%
so he was delayed for a few days.

00:36:04.310 --> 00:36:06.600 line:80%
He will return
once he finishes investigating.

00:36:06.600 --> 00:36:07.720 line:80%
General He,

00:36:09.120 --> 00:36:11.290 line:80%
stop protecting your good student.

00:36:11.310 --> 00:36:13.440 line:80%
A sixth-rank commandant

00:36:13.870 --> 00:36:16.800 line:80%
going to a remote backwater town
to capture bandits?

00:36:17.990 --> 00:36:19.310 line:80%
He clearly wants to use this chance

00:36:19.310 --> 00:36:21.040 line:80%
to smear the Wei family's name.

00:36:22.030 --> 00:36:24.230 line:80%
Watch your words, Eldest Young Master.

00:36:24.560 --> 00:36:25.470 line:80%
Eldest Young Master,

00:36:25.470 --> 00:36:28.310 line:80%
you already control
the military in Yanzhou.

00:36:28.990 --> 00:36:30.680 line:80%
Why did you suddenly change course

00:36:30.680 --> 00:36:33.080 line:80%
and come here to Jizhou?

00:36:35.870 --> 00:36:37.870 line:80%
Xie Zheng has always been arrogant.

00:36:38.470 --> 00:36:41.430 line:80%
Naturally, his soldiers
don't listen to orders.

00:36:43.120 --> 00:36:44.470 line:80%
If I go to take over...

00:36:46.330 --> 00:36:48.390 line:80%
I'm afraid something might go wrong.

00:36:50.980 --> 00:36:51.770 line:80%
General He.

00:36:53.350 --> 00:36:56.320 line:80%
Subdue Xie Zheng's Yanzhou troops for me.

00:36:56.520 --> 00:36:57.800 line:80%
Then we'll press on

00:36:57.800 --> 00:36:59.730 line:80%
and take Prince Changxin's Chongzhou City.

00:36:59.730 --> 00:37:00.810 line:80%
Once we succeed,

00:37:01.720 --> 00:37:04.450 line:80%
we'll be the greatest heroes
in my father's eyes.

00:37:09.640 --> 00:37:10.840 line:80%
Eldest Young Master,

00:37:11.120 --> 00:37:14.760 line:80%
Prince Changxin suffered setbacks
against the Marquis of Wu'an.

00:37:14.760 --> 00:37:16.490 line:80%
He lost several major battles,

00:37:16.650 --> 00:37:18.250 line:80%
and retreated to Chongzhou,

00:37:18.830 --> 00:37:21.070 line:80%
but his main force is intact,

00:37:21.160 --> 00:37:23.090 line:80%
and he still has capable generals.

00:37:23.200 --> 00:37:25.560 line:80%
Eldest Young Master,
you've traveled a long way.

00:37:25.560 --> 00:37:27.760 line:80%
We shouldn't rush into battle.

00:37:27.830 --> 00:37:28.960 line:80%
Quite the opposite.

00:37:29.560 --> 00:37:32.030 line:80%
Prince Changxin
has lost consecutive battles,

00:37:32.030 --> 00:37:33.240 line:80%
and the Chongzhou army's morale is low.

00:37:33.240 --> 00:37:35.170 line:80%
This is the perfect time to strike!

00:37:39.080 --> 00:37:39.910 line:80%
General He,

00:37:40.470 --> 00:37:43.270 line:80%
I respect you as a veteran general
under my father,

00:37:43.390 --> 00:37:45.770 line:80%
which is why I came here personally.

00:37:46.470 --> 00:37:47.640 line:80%
This is an order,

00:37:48.200 --> 00:37:49.200 line:80%
not a suggestion.

00:37:53.510 --> 00:37:55.710 line:80%
I expect your cooperation, General He.

00:38:11.450 --> 00:38:13.870 line:80%
[Chongde Hall]

00:38:11.800 --> 00:38:12.930 line:80%
Prime Minister Wei!

00:38:15.870 --> 00:38:17.600 line:80%
What is the matter, Grand Tutor?

00:38:17.600 --> 00:38:18.600 line:80%
Prime Minister Wei,

00:38:18.600 --> 00:38:20.200 line:80%
in the Battle of Jinzhou years ago,

00:38:20.200 --> 00:38:21.720 line:80%
General Xie died in battle.

00:38:21.720 --> 00:38:22.830 line:80%
More than a decade later,

00:38:22.830 --> 00:38:25.560 line:80%
the fate of the Marquis of Wu'an
is still unknown.

00:38:25.800 --> 00:38:29.200 line:80%
Yet you still sent your only heir

00:38:29.200 --> 00:38:30.640 line:80%
to the Northwest.

00:38:31.640 --> 00:38:33.890 line:80%
When it comes to loyalty to Great Yin,

00:38:34.390 --> 00:38:37.720 line:80%
no one compares to you,
Prime Minister Wei.

00:38:38.200 --> 00:38:39.680 line:80%
There is an ancient saying:

00:38:39.680 --> 00:38:41.280 line:80%
"Though our country is vast,

00:38:41.280 --> 00:38:42.940 line:80%
not an inch shall be yielded."

00:38:43.080 --> 00:38:46.940 line:80%
The sons of the Wei and Xie families
can die on the battlefield for this

00:38:47.280 --> 00:38:48.830 line:80%
with no regrets.

00:38:50.080 --> 00:38:53.940 line:80%
Then we shall await the triumphant return
of Eldest Young Master Wei.

00:38:54.350 --> 00:38:58.280 line:80%
I congratulate you in advance.

00:38:59.990 --> 00:39:02.030 line:80%
Then I must also congratulate you,
Grand Tutor.

00:39:02.030 --> 00:39:05.470 line:80%
Your grandson has been promoted
to Martial Commandant.

00:39:05.640 --> 00:39:08.200 line:80%
Sending him to the Northwest
for training at such a young age

00:39:08.200 --> 00:39:10.200 line:80%
was great foresight.

00:39:10.870 --> 00:39:12.080 line:80%
When he returns,

00:39:12.830 --> 00:39:15.160 line:80%
he will surely be a pillar of the state.

00:39:17.990 --> 00:39:21.390 line:80%
For 16 years,
my original intention has not changed.

00:39:21.390 --> 00:39:23.120 line:80%
I work solely for Great Yin.

00:39:23.600 --> 00:39:25.080 line:80%
I am open and honorable.

00:39:25.520 --> 00:39:27.150 line:80%
Open and honorable?

00:39:27.680 --> 00:39:29.480 line:80%
The Grand Tutor from 16 years ago

00:39:29.800 --> 00:39:33.160 line:80%
could not bear the weight of those words.

00:39:41.470 --> 00:39:42.080 line:80%
Hey...

00:39:42.430 --> 00:39:44.160 line:80%
The Northwest Army
belongs to the Great Yin Dynasty.

00:39:44.160 --> 00:39:46.910 line:80%
Does he think the Northwest
is the Wei family's backyard?

00:39:46.910 --> 00:39:49.160 line:80%
Wei Yan is too arrogant.

00:40:28.200 --> 00:40:30.030 line:80%
[To Prime Minister Wei of Great Yin]

00:40:30.200 --> 00:40:32.600 line:80%
It is time to hand it over.

00:40:31.420 --> 00:40:33.290 line:80%
[To Prime Minister Wei of Great Yin]

00:40:34.030 --> 00:40:36.280 line:80%
When you handed it to me back then,

00:40:36.280 --> 00:40:38.140 line:80%
you knew this day would come.

00:40:39.510 --> 00:40:41.120 line:80%
You wanted me

00:40:40.900 --> 00:40:45.130 line:80%
[To Prime Minister Wei of Great Yin]

00:40:41.560 --> 00:40:43.760 line:80%
to take good care of your two daughters.

00:40:46.390 --> 00:40:47.500 line:80%
Pei Yi.

00:40:48.470 --> 00:40:50.040 line:80%
This is urgent.

00:40:50.390 --> 00:40:53.120 line:80%
Deliver this to Prime Minister Wei
immediately.

00:40:53.510 --> 00:40:54.080 line:80%
Yes, sir.

00:41:01.800 --> 00:41:02.680 line:80%
Come out.

00:41:03.350 --> 00:41:05.350 line:80%
At the council hall this afternoon,

00:41:05.560 --> 00:41:08.430 line:80%
I knew you were hiding nearby.

00:41:13.570 --> 00:41:15.590 line:80%
I was afraid I came at the wrong time.

00:41:16.080 --> 00:41:18.190 line:80%
After all, my identity is sensitive.

00:41:18.510 --> 00:41:19.420 line:80%
Wenkan,

00:41:20.310 --> 00:41:21.910 line:80%
I sent you to suppress bandits.

00:41:21.910 --> 00:41:23.510 line:80%
What is there to be afraid of?

00:41:24.680 --> 00:41:26.950 line:80%
I am worried that my identity
as a member of the Li family

00:41:26.950 --> 00:41:28.680 line:80%
will bring criticism upon you.

00:41:28.760 --> 00:41:30.350 line:80%
In front of Prime Minister Wei,

00:41:30.350 --> 00:41:32.080 line:80%
it would just add to the gossip.

00:41:34.560 --> 00:41:35.560 line:80%
Wenkan,

00:41:36.560 --> 00:41:38.120 line:80%
count carefully.

00:41:38.720 --> 00:41:40.720 line:80%
How many years have you been with me?

00:41:40.910 --> 00:41:42.800 line:80%
Since I came to the Northwest as a child

00:41:42.800 --> 00:41:45.130 line:80%
and learning military strategy from you,

00:41:45.310 --> 00:41:47.510 line:80%
it has been 16 years.

00:41:49.430 --> 00:41:50.960 line:80%
Then you should know that

00:41:51.910 --> 00:41:53.470 line:80%
in my eyes,

00:41:54.160 --> 00:41:57.310 line:80%
there is no conflict
between the Li and Wei families.

00:41:57.640 --> 00:42:00.310 line:80%
There is only the army of Great Yin

00:42:00.600 --> 00:42:02.160 line:80%
and the people of Great Yin.

00:42:02.990 --> 00:42:06.130 line:80%
If you have a clear conscience,

00:42:06.240 --> 00:42:09.910 line:80%
there is no need to avoid suspicion
because of your surname.

00:42:13.540 --> 00:42:14.250 line:80%
By the way,

00:42:14.950 --> 00:42:17.830 line:80%
have you made any progress
on the matter I asked you to investigate?

00:42:17.830 --> 00:42:18.830 line:80%
I discovered

00:42:18.950 --> 00:42:21.990 line:80%
Prime Minister Wei's Suicide Warriors
raided the Fan family twice.

00:42:21.990 --> 00:42:23.800 line:80%
They are obviously looking for something.

00:42:23.800 --> 00:42:24.800 line:80%
Fortunately,

00:42:25.030 --> 00:42:26.690 line:80%
Mrs. Fan was not harmed.

00:42:26.880 --> 00:42:27.910 line:80%
However, they already have thoughts

00:42:27.910 --> 00:42:29.120 line:80%
of leaving Lin'an.

00:42:29.830 --> 00:42:31.990 line:80%
I stopped them under the pretext
of investigating the case.

00:42:31.990 --> 00:42:33.800 line:80%
I have asked Zhuoran
to protect them in secret.

00:42:33.800 --> 00:42:34.950 line:80%
It is safer this way.

00:42:35.410 --> 00:42:38.830 line:80%
How are Mrs. Fan and her sister doing?

00:42:39.350 --> 00:42:41.200 line:80%
They make a living butchering pigs.

00:42:41.200 --> 00:42:42.660 line:80%
She just took a husband in.

00:42:44.510 --> 00:42:45.120 line:80%
Master,

00:42:46.160 --> 00:42:48.720 line:80%
I have a lead on another matter.

00:42:52.470 --> 00:42:53.800 line:80%
If the Marquis of Wu'an

00:42:54.310 --> 00:42:55.530 line:80%
truly were alive,

00:42:55.990 --> 00:42:56.680 line:80%
what should we do?